  2  FROM Orderr o
  3  JOIN OrderItemLine ol USING (order_id)
  4  JOIN Product p Using (product_id)
  5  WHERE product_name = 'Sony Camera' AND order_date BETWEEN TO_DATE('01-05-2023','DD-MM-YYYY') AND TO_DATE('28-05-2023','DD-MM-YYYY');

  2  FROM Customer c

  4   LEFT JOIN Orderr o USING (order_id);

SQL> SELECT customer_id, c.customer_name, c.customer_address, c.customer_categories, o.order_date, order_id
  2  FROM Customer c
  3  JOIN CustomerOrder co USING (customer_id)
  4  JOIN Orderr o USING (order_id)
  5  WHERE order_date = (SELECT MAX(order_date) from Orderr);

SQL> SELECT TO_CHAR(order_date, 'MONTH') AS MONTH, SUM (total_order_amount) AS TOTAL_REVENUE_OF_COMPANY
  2  FROM Orderr
  3  GROUP BY TO_CHAR(order_date, 'MONTH');

SQL> SELECT vendor_id, v.vendor_name, v.vendor_address, v.vendor_contact_number, COUNT (p.product_id) AS Supply_Count
  2  FROM Vendor v
  3  JOIN Product p USING (vendor_id)
  4  GROUP BY vendor_id, vendor_name, vendor_address, vendor_contact_number
  5  HAVING COUNT(p.product_id) > 3;

SQL> SELECT customer_id, customer_name, customer_address,TO_CHAR(order_date,'MONTH') AS Month, COUNT(order_id) AS order_count, SUM(total_order_amount) AS total_spending
  2  FROM customer
  3  JOIN customerorder USING (customer_id)
  4  JOIN orderr USING (order_id)
  5  WHERE TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(order_date, 'MONTH'), 'MONTH') = TO_DATE('AUGUST', 'MONTH')
  6  GROUP BY customer_id, customer_name, customer_address,to_char(order_date,'MONTH')
  7  HAVING COUNT(order_id) = (SELECT MAX(COUNT(order_id)) AS order_count FROM orderitemline GROUP BY order_id)
  8  ORDER BY order_count DESC;

no rows selected

  3  where to_date(to_char(order_date,'MONTH'),'MONTH') = TO_DATE ('august','MONTH')
  4  GROUP BY (customer_id, customer_name, customer_address, customer_categories,to_char(order_date,'MONTH'))
  5   HAVING COUNT(order_id) = (SELECT MAX(order_count) FROM (SELECT COUNT(order_id) AS order_count FROM orderquantity GROUP BY order_id))ORDER BY order_count DESC;

SQL> insert into customerorder VALUES (101,409);

1 row created.

SQL> SELECT customer_id, customer_name, customer_address,TO_CHAR(order_date,'MONTH') AS Month, COUNT(order_id) AS order_count, SUM(total_order_amount) AS total_spending FROM customer JOIN customerorder USING (customer_id) JOIN orderr USING (order_id)WHERE TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(order_date, 'MONTH'), 'MONTH') = TO_DATE('AUGUST', 'MONTH') GROUP BY customer_id, customer_name, customer_address,to_char(order_date,'MONTH') HAVING COUNT(order_id) = (SELECT MAX(COUNT(order_id)) AS order_count FROM orderitemline GROUP BY order_id) ORDER BY order_count DESC;

SQL> SELECT customer_id, customer_name, customer_address,TO_CHAR(order_date,'MONTH') AS Month, COUNT(order_id) AS order_count, SUM(total_order_amount) AS total_spending
  2  FROM customer JOIN customerorder USING (customer_id) JOIN orderr USING (order_id)
  3  WHERE TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(order_date, 'MONTH'), 'MONTH') = TO_DATE('AUGUST', 'MONTH')
  4  GROUP BY customer_id, customer_name, customer_address,to_char(order_date,'MONTH')
  5   HAVING COUNT(order_id) = (SELECT MAX(COUNT(order_id)) AS order_count FROM orderitemline GROUP BY order_id) ORDER BY order_count DESC;
